commit.message: Fix help docs on __bool__ to backquote operators for docs
Update github repo name to python-tribool
Drop Python 3.2 from Tox testing (virtualenv no longer supports Python 3.0-3.2)
Remove __index__ definition (tuple inheritance makes it redundant)
Update tests to expect TypeError rather than ValueError
Change __nonzero__, __bool__ and __index__ to raise TypeError (rather than ValueError)
Remove __trunc__ method and adjust whitespace to please pylint
Update imports, shorten description, and change license
Remove shlex import and CamelCase htmlhelp_basename
Update README (keep in sync with docs/index.rst)
Update docs regarding singleton pattern enforcement
Modify Tribool to inherit from tuple to prevent mutation of its internal state
Implement __reduce__ so pickle obeys singleton pattern
